divs: Sighting DetailsMe and my girlfriend were riding home in her car at 1am, going north. We noticed 3 sequentially flashing lights, at first we almost thought it was a radio tower until it started to very slowly, move downward. Then it started moving perpendicularly to it's previous path at a pretty quick pace. It continued until it was obscured my trees.I have personally witnessed two other undeniable UFO's so I was very excited to see this phenomenom.
